headline: Camden Property Trust Announces Fourth Quarter 2025 Earnings Release and Conference Call Dates
summary: HOUSTON, January 12, 2026--Camden Property Trust (NYSE:CPT) (the "Company") announced today that its fourth quarter 2025 earnings will be released after the market closes on Thursday, February 5, 2026. Management will host a conference call on the following day, Friday, February 6, 2026, at 10:00 AM Central Time.
